AllocationListingCurrencySummaryForReportForm is a SummaryForm
    title is "_"
    Layout
        three column
            column1 of 50%
                text of "<AllocationRun>_Total"
                    bold
                blank line
            column2
                DerivedCurrencyReportTotalPostTo
                    label is "PostTo"
                    display when blank
                DerivedCurrencyReportTotalPostFrom
                    label is "PostFrom"
                    display when blank
            column3
                visible when (not IsUnits)
                    CurrencyCode
                    CurrencyCode
